    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诺兰岭:</strong> 曾经辉煌的大都市，现在笼罩在有毒的坟墓中，野心和复仇的见证。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你是游牧者</strong>，混乱的受害者，被城市的绝望呼声和祖父的耳语驱使。破碎的记忆点燃了你的目标，燃烧你的战斗力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/01a740888f256d30dc0a36205391b030.poster.avif?t=1758651407\" width=760 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/01a740888f256d30dc0a36205391b030.webm?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/01a740888f256d30dc0a36205391b030.mp4?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭露阴谋:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不被发现的情况下，破解能量塔以进入限制区，解开笼罩诺兰岭灭亡的错综复杂的欺骗网络。解读神秘的信息，这些信息编织了科学傲慢、积怨和一个曾经伟大城市的悲惨衰落的故事。听听城市最后的痛苦哭声和腐败公司的寒冷宣言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控城市丛林:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你在屋顶生存中磨练出来的跑酷技能 - <u><strong>攀爬墙壁，用抓钩发射自己，以闪电般的速度冲刺，并用滑行动作挑战重力，在危险的环境和腐朽的建筑中导航</strong></u>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴森的雾气在废弃的城市街道上弥漫。它们是被遗忘的记忆碎片，还是寻找安慰的幽灵？跟随它们的幽灵踪迹来磨练你的跑酷技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/6ea43ea97c423e3ad0a5b1a123460f4a.poster.avif?t=1758651407\" width=760 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/6ea43ea97c423e3ad0a5b1a123460f4a.webm?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/6ea43ea97c423e3ad0a5b1a123460f4a.mp4?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >船长的堕落:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个被风暴抛弃的船长将他的船撞向诺兰岭的最高安全监狱，携带着一个神秘的脉动水晶。被误认为逃犯，他释放了水晶的能量来换取自由。被挫折和怨恨吞噬，他变成了一个渴望权力的疯子，占领了监狱，然后是整个城市。但他的统治付出了可怕的代价：他依赖水晶生存，将城市笼罩在只有变种人才能呼吸的有毒云中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变种混乱:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滥用水晶的力量带来了可怕的后果。变种囚犯现在自由漫游，被船长的影响驱使的扭曲怪物。他们针对任何试图反对他议程的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阴影中的希望:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>利用阴影来取得优势。</strong></u> 无人察觉地跟踪你的猎物，并释放毁灭性的隐身攻击以消灭变种威胁。每消灭一个敌人，他们对城市的控制就会减弱，为你的最终对决铺平战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/75624ca46014f4f2e4fa4f4085ed28b9.poster.avif?t=1758651407\" width=760 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/75624ca46014f4f2e4fa4f4085ed28b9.webm?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067620/extras/75624ca46014f4f2e4fa4f4085ed28b9.mp4?t=1758651407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会尊重祖父的遗产，成为希望的灯塔吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诺兰岭的命运掌握在你手中。</p>",
